cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
This a super reliable, reasonably priced, 2005 Nissan Maxima with 100,000 miles on it. Leather seats, seat warmers, sun-roof, and power everything.
A well maintained 2006 Nissan Altima with 130,000 miles on it. Needs a little work but runs great.
